### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Rich vehicle retrieval tests
### Each query should hit a different chunk type
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### ── 1. Performance chunk (:2)
### Expected: engine, hp, torque, 0-60
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/bmw-m3-2025-competition/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What engine does the M3 use and how fast is it?",
  "topK": 2,
  "mode": "HYBRID"
}

###

### ── 2. Ownership cost chunk (:3)
### Expected: fuel cost, insurance, depreciation, 5-year total
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/bmw-m3-2025-competition/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "How much does it cost to own the M3 over 5 years?",
  "topK": 2,
  "mode": "HYBRID"
}

###

### ── 3. Rankings chunk (:4)
### Expected: US News rank 2nd of 18, Car and Driver editors choice
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/bmw-m3-2025-competition/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "How does the M3 rank compared to other sports sedans?",
  "topK": 2,
  "mode": "HYBRID"
}

###

### ── 4. Safety chunk (:5)
### Expected: NHTSA 5-star, IIHS Good, AEB standard
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/bmw-m3-2025-competition/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What are the safety ratings for the M3?",
  "topK": 2,
  "mode": "HYBRID"
}

###

### ── 5. Maintenance chunk (:12 = 30k service)
### Expected: brake pads, $950 dealer, $420 DIY
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/bmw-m3-2025-competition/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What does the 30000 mile service cost at the dealer?",
  "topK": 2,
  "mode": "HYBRID"
}

###

### ── 6. Recall chunk (:20 or :21)
### Expected: adaptive cruise recall, fuel injector recall
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/bmw-m3-2025-competition/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Are there any open recalls on the M3?",
  "topK": 3,
  "mode": "HYBRID"
}

###

### ── 7. Reviews chunk (:7)
### Expected: Car and Driver 9/10, Motor Trend 9/10, pros/cons
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/bmw-m3-2025-competition/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What do expert reviewers say about the M3?",
  "topK": 2,
  "mode": "HYBRID"
}

###

### ── 8. Cross-chunk query — should fuse performance + cost
### Expected: answer references both engine AND ownership cost
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/bmw-m3-2025-competition/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Is the M3 worth the price given its performance?",
  "topK": 3,
  "mode": "HYBRID"
}

###

### ── 9. Fleet search — maintenance cost across all vehicles
### Expected: BMW M3 chunks surface for maintenance queries
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "which vehicles have the highest maintenance costs",
  "topK": 3
}
